display_long_description:
Set yourself up and experience the best bowling game on your device.

This additive virtual bowling game will compel you to spend your maximum time on the game for a long time. Whether you are a pro player or playing it for the first time, this game is for everyone. 
Pick the ball and win the battle, check the LIVE score, and get your name on the list of top players.

Key features:
- Latest theme and playing area to feel the real experience of bowling game
- DJ Bonnie to enhance entertainment
- Selection of the right Avatar from the available icons
- Offline play support
- Scoreboard to analyze the score 
- Single-user play mode
- Game user manual for better understanding
- VR remote control for taking the correct direction
- There are three different playing levels: Easy, Medium, and Hard
- High-quality graphics to experience the realistic scenario
- Reset option to reset all your scores

Let's see how many strikes you can score consecutively.  Relax your mind in your leisure time.

Download it now!
